| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1662 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5add4b47-fbac-5720-a3b9-8b2f79b3486c"
